\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Me father. Me brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have any other musical instruments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh? Me dad? Yes, he had a - what are them things, them long things with the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9700648\charrsid15683539 mouthpiece}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  on with a - were they called flutes.
