\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, and he had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9700648\charrsid15683539 melodeon}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 . So he was quite old fashioned. And he was a good singer.
