\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9700648\charrsid15683539 They\rquote re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  gone you know, she's another wife. They would get it. And Things a Lady Would Like. And oh it was a lovely book.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were there any newspapers in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, there was always newspapers, I couldn't tell you what sort.
