\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Just people like myself. You know, happy people. Clean }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 living}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  people I say.
