\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I call him a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 snob}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
