\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10364370\charrsid15683539 only}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  school I went to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How old were you when you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I was about a month - I was about twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I think so. Think if me father could have done without but he couldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you attend any part time education afterwards, did you go to any evening classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, we used to go night school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How old would you be then, would it be just after leaving school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Just after leaving the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did you go for, what did you go to learn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well you could learn sewing, anything you - you put your name down for you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did you go for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh - I couldn't tell you now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I never bothered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I must have done. I'm never stuck at any time. I must have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You left school in 1903, what was your first full time job? You say you stayed at home to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 "Til I was sixteen. I was home 'til I was sixteen. And I started working -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When your father married again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you not get on with your step-mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I got on with her all right but - it just - a family affair, that's a thing you keep to yourself. Oh no, I would - I would have gon
e if - after - when she came in house I would have got out, I was old enough for that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So y-u got a job when you were sixteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. That was me full time job 'til I was married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What was your job, you were in a tobacco factory?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. Co-operative - Tobacco. It doesn't sound nice, factories, but it was a - just same as being in a shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What were you doing there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we were doing - twist and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10364370\charrsid15683539 t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 arget and - f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10364370\charrsid15683539 rom}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  them you see to - I went right from the beginning to the end, 
I couldn't tell you all the stages. I started at the bottom and went to counter hand. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 All just making cigarettes was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, we didn't make cigarettes. Se made - Target, Ladies Twist, Middle Brown. Deep Brown. Scented Bar. But cigarettes th
e boys made on their own. The }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 younger}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  lads you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have to treat it as it came in, could you describe your job, any of the jobs that you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. It come in Hogs heads, you'll not understand what a hog's head is? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 
Oh I couldn't tell you, it was - it's a huge thing, a round. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
It used to take so many men to get it - they had the slide off the van you know. The Co-operative stores were at the front but we were at the back you see. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 
It used to have to be slid up - there and they would bring what we call eight hogs' heads, someone might know. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 they}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 - the - eight would fill this kitchen, this - and - we used to piece it up and it was all leaf inside. Well we'd - we had it to strip. To stalk. Stalks }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 this look. Everything. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 There}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  like wheelers, pointers, spinners. That's the work. The men spin you see. But it's all done by electric now, you can't see that now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 It would be interesting to do wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well it was tiring.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 get this}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh through the Co-operative }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 store}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 . }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 See we were buying our house through it.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So you just went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 And applied and I got it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What hours did you work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we worked - we worked from eight o'clock on a morning 'til five on a night. That was for four and six a w
eek. And we walked three mile to work and three mile back. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where was the store then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Bishop Auckland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you work on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Worked on a Saturday from - eight 'til twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have a half day apart from Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You were paid four and six?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Four and six a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No I didn't. No. Well when I got to - to counter hand I only had nine and six And 
I'd been there seven years. And gone from the bottom, that was the top wage. I got married when I was twenty-three, I was there from sixteen. We had some happy times. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were they nice girls that you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes. They're nearly all 
gone now. Oh yes. What one did another did. And all decent respectable girls you know. Mr Tait wouldn't have had them otherwise.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you give any of this four and six in at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, all of it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What was it spent }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 on?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Eeh - I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did you get back then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 About sixpence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did you spend your sixpence on?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Me father clothes us mind, he bought all our clothes. What did I spend it on? Why it was - sweets. No, you - we used to go and - and do - I'm te
lling you wrong there Doris, we used to go to penny readings. And we used to go from there to a fish shop. You got a fish and chips for threepence. We used to go from there to Wiper's and get a quarter of sweets and we were done for a week. That was your 
money gone. But you couldn't get fish and chips now for threepence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you get on with the other people you worked with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh fine. Fine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did your employer treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh fine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you feel about him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 He was all right was Mr Tait. He was a grand man. He went from us to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 
Sinclair\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 . He'll be dead now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you feel about the work, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, I liked it. I liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You kept this job up 'til you were married in 1914?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you do any other jobs when you were married, up to the end of the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Have you done any jobs since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. Me husband wouldn't let me. I had the chance but he wouldn't let me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Would you have preferred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I was quite happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you serve an apprenticeship or a training period for this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No. They set you off at the bottom and you worked it up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you belong to a trade union at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you feel }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 that}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  employers and workers had the same interests or different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I think we were all alike. All happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among workers, some people say that in those days the
re was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers, did you feel that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. And there was four trained men with us you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 But you got on all right with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh fine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Did you continue to live at home after you left school, you did until you were sixteen didn't you, you still lived at home until you were married didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your parents at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I was never in to make any difference. Just to sleep.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did it alter your attitude to your brother and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we were all separated up you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So when your father married again you stayed at home but you went out to work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 'Til I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 was}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
 married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What happened to the rest of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 The other sister went to service and me brother went to live with me auntie. And me young sister was with me au
nt - another auntie from me mother dying. Me young sister.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you spend your Sunday any differently after you left school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, weren't allowed to, it had to be Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You still went to chapel after you left school did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 After I left school? Of course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You still went to Sunday school did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you take an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time, did you continue to spend yo
ur spare time in the same way or did you do different things now, afteryou }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 left}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
 school? You got a bicycle, did you go cycling at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, with me husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Before you married him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you anything else differently how you'd left school and were in your teens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You went to Redcar with the persons you worked with, what was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh that was three girls that was serving their time to be dressmakers. Yes, we all used to go together. Our holidays. But they didn't wor
k with me. They were working for different firms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 But you went on holiday with them in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 They were your friends were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you go out in the evening at all and where did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 Oh - we put our time in when we were at seaside, I couldn't tell you where we would be.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you were at home where would you go in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 On }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 an}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
 evening? Well we used to - have Bible Class on a Monday night, you've got that. The penny readings and choir. We put our time in all right. It - we had to in a village like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Who were you friendly with, these girls that you went on holiday with, and you got to know some boys at this time did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 We would know a dozen or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Weren't there any new friends that you made at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I thought you got to know your husband about this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh no, they weren't with me when I got to know me husband. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When would you get to know these girls that you went away with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I'd known them all my life. I used to go to their house you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So you didn't make any new friends after you left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You got to know some boys at this stage, you used to go to night school and all the rest of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh aye, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you meet the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 After - after school come out, night school. We would be sewing, they would be at the other school, we could see them. Just kiddy like.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you ever bring friends home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Certain ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Would that be girls or boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well there would be a bit of both I mean.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have any special friends at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. Yes I had. I was in fever hospital, I got to know a friend there and we were friends 'til she died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When did you go in the fever hospital?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I was only young.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you got to know some boys where would you all go together, the boys and girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh just round the streets, we never went out of the streets. Just talking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you used to go cycling where did you go cycling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh - Barnard Castle and Winston and round about nearly every time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Who would go with you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Me husband. Me - young man were then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did your father meet your friends at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. He knew them all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did your father expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have to be home at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What time }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 do you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  have to be home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 We all had to be in before ten Doris. Else he'd be after us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What age were you married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Twenty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 And that was 1914?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 11th of April.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 long had}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  you known your husband then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 About five year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Now how cou
ld I tell you that? Well a friend and I were walk - out for a walk. And my husband was standing where we had to pass. And I said, oh Francis, what a good looking lad. Just like that. And she says, now go on, I'm not going to invite you - introduce you bec
ause, she says, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
 should know him, he lived along you - against you long enough. I didn't know him. So I said to her after we got away past him I said, bet you I could walk out with him. Eeh, she says, you won't. I said, I will. Just - you know, daredevil
 like. So her and her young man was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 going}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 Hippodrome}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
. I was wanting to go to Bishop Auckland and who comes and opens the gate for me that I couldn't open but him. So he went with me. And I stayed with him. Yes, just like that. Yes. He told me years afte
r - oh - there was a Mrs Wormald used to live against me says she was - she used to say to me, now Bob, that's your wife going out. And he - he didn't know me and I didn't know him. She used to say, that'll be - she was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 fortune}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  teller. Yes. Wormald. Worm
ald. And she prophesied I would be his wife and I didn't know him. And I did marry him you know. And first time we met they both started to laugh and I said, what's wrong. And he wouldn't tell me. ten he said, she said you would be my wife. I says, oh, sh
e's been reading cards again, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where did your husband come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 A place called Broughton. Near Pickering.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you save up money before getting married or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did your father help you in setting up a home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 He had to, I had an invalid husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What happened just after you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Well our names had been in church a fortnight, they'd been called out twice. And he fell off work. And he was off work off and on for a year. And he'd never ailed any
thing in his life. But understand he'd been a footman before that. Then he come away from being a gentleman into a mine. And - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 whether}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  it was that or not but a soldier got over it. He didn't have it any more.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 It was just that twelve months then you'd have a struggle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 First year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 During this time you say your brother helped you a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Well you only had five or six sick money coming in then. I had the rent to pay you know. 'Cos I was in me uncle's house and - didn't help me any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How long were you engaged, were you engaged at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh - we'd quite made it up at start. We didn't bother - I had a ring mind. But - we knew from beginning we would get married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How long did you have a ring for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I don't know. I couldn't t
ell you Doris, I had one long enough. I had two. I lost one - no, I didn't - I did lost it but I know who has it. Lost it but I know who had it. Yes. And - she was told but she kept it. It was somebody we were very friendly with. And he went and got me an
other one. He spoiled me you know. He did spoil me. Oh he spoiled me Doris, it wasn't a bit of good, I just took things for granted. You know, if I didn't - if I wanted - before I were married. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 I'd just say - if I mentioned if it was there, you know. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I oft 
think, eeh I was mean. You know. But I - he made up for it after. I used to say, the good old scrooge. I used to call him all sorts, poor lad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How many years would you say you were engaged, two or three?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I should think two. Definitely like. We made our minds up before that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Could you describe the wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
The wedding? Now how do you want me to describe that? Nothing in particular, he was ill - when we went to church. Could hardly walk to church, up church path.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have many people there, many guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, we had our family gathering. They always had in them days, boiled a couple of hams.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You did the entertaining at home did you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yourselves, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you get any nice presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes. We got heaps of presents. 'Course we were a big family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have a honeymoon, did you go away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I went straight into my own house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What address was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 4 Cross Row, St Helens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How many years did you live there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Then where did you move to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Shildon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were you at Shildon at the end of the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 That\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  where Freda was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What was the address at Shildon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 34 - 35 George Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 And you were there 'til the war finished?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. Then the company moved us to Darlington.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How old was your husband when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Twenty-seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What was your husband's job when you married, he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5798061\charrsid15683539 miner}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  by then was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he have any other jobs before he became a miner, you said he was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 f}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 ootman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Well - he was just relief - he was - he went from hall boy right up you see. But - he used to help the butler. So - he was like a footman, he was a help you see, all the way through.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where was he working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Boyington Hall. Boyington Hall. Yorkshire. Many windows as the days and years. He used to say that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How long had he been down the mine when you married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Not long. He come out the year we were married. Couldn't stay.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Then what did he do afterwards then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Railway. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 Shildon}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  shops. He was there 'til he died - for the company.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 With British Railway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Mm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did he do there in the railway workshop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I couldn't tell you. He was where they were breaking up things up and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was it skilled or semi-skilled would you say? Was it a skilled job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No. He was just too late, if he'd got started he would have been a riveter but - he did riveting when there was spare men you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So he stayed in the railway workshops right up 'til he retired?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Until he retired.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he ever do any casual or part time jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How do you think your husband felt about his work, did he like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 yes,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
 he li}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 k}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 ed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he like being a miner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well he broke down in health, he wasn't there long.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have any children, you had three didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 But not for years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you just have three, did you lose any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. I had none 'til I had Freda. I was twenty-nine when I had our Freda.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What would her date of birth be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 31st of July.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 1920?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I was twenty-nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you know how much your husband earned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How much of that would he give to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 He give me the lot, he always did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did you give him back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Well sometimes if I was hard run I would - he would just take his tobacco out of it and - as hilling or two for match, football match, he was content.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you discuss with your husband how the money should be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No, he had the good faith in me. He never asked - never bothered. No. We hadn't big wages you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You were married in 1914 and you lived two years in Cross Row?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. And then to Shildon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How many rooms were in the house at Shildon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Two bedrooms, a kitchen and a scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were they any relatives or lodgers living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have any paid help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was the washing done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You did it did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you make or mend any of your clothes r your husband's clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I had to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well everything like everyone else. Either knit or sew, anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have new clothes or secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Never secondhand clothes, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where would you buy your new clothes, do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Co-operative Stores. Oh, when I was married? Oh I bought them at Wilkinson's of Bishop Auckland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 And they were always new when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Do you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 know}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  when you had new clothes when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Mine was new clothes when I was married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Any particular time of the year when you had new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was there any particular time - well we always used to get them at Easter. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How about the shoes, did your husband mend the shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 Were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  your shoes now new or secondhand?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh always new stuff for us.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where would you buy the shoes from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we used to get them all over, sometimes at Talland's, sometimes at Co-operative Stores. Talland'. Talland's - Tommy Talland's.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have new shoes at any particular time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 A good pair at winter and a pair of light ones in summer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 For the first year your husband was ill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did your husband help you with jobs in the house, did he ever help you with the cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well there was no need to. He was out all day you see, I had all me time to myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he ever help with the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Or the washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. Oh yes. Yes. He would mind the baby while I washed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 about}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
 the washing up, did he help you with the washing up at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he light the fires for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he do any decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he do any repairs to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 He needn't to really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was it a railway house?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. It was a private house on mortgage.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did he do any improvements to the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes, he would do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Could you tell me where the meals were eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were there any occasions when you ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. If I felt I wanted food in the front room I would sit in there, but there was a scullery you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You had a scullery as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we called th
at the kitchen. The scullery and the pantry you see. We used to put a table under that window there. And the set pots was there you see, what you boiled your clothes in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So which room did you most often have your meals in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 In the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 kitchen}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 . That's the - the scullery now we call it. Keeps the place tidy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 But occasionally }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  ate in the front room, when would that be, any special time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, no special time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Can you remember any time when you did eat in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 front}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, just when I felt like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where did you do your cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 And you had a kitchen range?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Not in the kitchen, it was in the living room, the range. Yes. Yes. You did all your cooking in there.
