I would say a teacake and bread and bread and butter and cheese, the ordinary plain tea. There'd be times I would have something likely cooked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have any supper at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. I went daft on fish and chips in them days. Eeh I was. He wouldn't have them though. He used to go for them for me.
