\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well he was in there a bit. And then they extended it, he was so - so well you know, he picked up so well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you go shopping together or anything on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 It would be Bishop Auckland we'd go to}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 gether }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 if there was anything, there was a market at Bishop Auckland. Then we used to walk the three miles for a walk out. And there were two traps to bring us back, threepence. Ho
rse and trap. There was no - old fashioned - trap for threepence, threepence three }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 miles}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 . Penny a mile. Old George Longstaffe.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How would you spend Sundays when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh tired. Having a lazy day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you carry on going to chapel when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No I didn't. I saw the kiddies went though. I'd go occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you think it wrong to work or enjoy yourself on a Sunday or did you think it didn't matter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I don't see there was anything wrong - I - I didn'
t believe in going gadding off on a Sunday like, you know what I mean, in them days. Many a time I look at them, I would tell me back but me father wouldn't allow you. And he wouldn't allow you to make a cake on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So how did you get on when you were married and had your own home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I just let it go, you know, you might go for a walk with dog or - it didn't matter what we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you mind doing any work on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I always used to make me own dinner and that. Probably of f
or a walk and come back and have a good tea. Then maybe old Bob and Freeman, the man }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 next door}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
, would go for another walk, the men you see. If not Mrs Freeman - us two we'd go together and go for another walk. We spent a lot of time in country, you know, walking about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You went to chapel occasionally when you were married but not often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Occasionally. You know when children come you - you get away from it somehow.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How often would you say you went when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I don't know. I wasn't married at chapel you know, I was married at church.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You were married in a church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was your husband a church man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 He was confirmed church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where were you married then, which church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 That was St Helens church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you ever go to church when you were married, did you ever go with your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Just if there were a funeral or a christening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So your husband didn't go regularly then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, he used to go with me. If we went anywhere, chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How often would you go to chapel would you say when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When I felt like it. Not very often. No. I think if people go away - you all get away. Oh at anniversaries or anything special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you belong to the choir after you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. 'Cos I dropped out of that, I lost - lost me voice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did the church or chapel run any temperance club when you were at Shildon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were you a member of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was it the one run by the chapel or was it the separate one you belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, it was a separate one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You still stayed in that when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 came}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So you didn't belong to one after you were married?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you belong to any other -clubs organized by the church or chapel after you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I couldn't say I was. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you had your own home was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. It's wrong you know. But I - I don't - unless we've company, then it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you yourself take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. I couldn't say I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Could you tell me what your views were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I was always Labour you know, always followed me dad and me husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Just because you were following them was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I followed somebody else, it wasn't that I was interested.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 So your husband was a Labour man as well was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. And his father wasn't you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Do you remember your husband voting in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What party would he vote for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 He would vote for Labour you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you vote in a general election before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 1918? Yes, I always use it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What party would you vote for?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I would vote for Labour. You can't go past your own class.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you or your husband ever feel under any pressure from anyone to vote for a particular party, from an employer or anybody like that?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Were you an actual member of a political party, you or your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you ever work for }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 one}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. Me father did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you take part in any political activity other than at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 election}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you and your husband were no
t doing your work how did you spend your time? How did you spend your free time, did you ever go out together in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You sometimes got together with the people next door did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh if I went out it would be up to me dad's or me brothers. They didn't live far from us you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you go out together at all in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Just Bishop Auckland,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What would you do there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Go to pictures. Only was pictures then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 About how often would you get out together at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh we didn't make a habit of going out every night. We - we made a habit of going out on a Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Where did you usually go on a Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Bishop Auckland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 That's when you went to the pictures?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. Pictures, penny readings or anything like this. It used to be pictures for him you know but not to others. That place is gone now.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What dime did your husband get home from work in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Five o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How many evenings a week would he spend at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 All of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did either of you go to any clubs, institutes or pubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No - he would go to go slip out if he wanted a drink but he didn't go very often.
