\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we shared them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did many neighbours drop in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, just the one. Next door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 That was any time was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you go out to visit friends or neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well I should think so. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
People often tell us that in those days they made their own amusement, what did you do when you got together with friends or neighbours, did you make music or play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes. We used to sit and play the piano and have a good sing. She was a singer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you ever play games with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Me father wouldn't allow us to have games.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh when I was married, no. No, I got away from me friends you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You say Nellie used to come when you were married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Oh aye, and - I worked in a roomful of girls, they used to visit me from in the place. But none of them lived in West Auckland. When I was married? Oh no, just me neighbours round about, I knew everybody round about.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you ever have a musical evening with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh no. Oh no. Just the Hippodrome on the Monday and Thursdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Who did you go to the Hippodrome with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Me neighbour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was your home rented at Shildon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you see anything of the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well he come to collect rents once a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you feel about him as a landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Poor fellow's gone. An old devil I said. He would take a ha'penny out of - you know. Oh, he was a nasty old man. He worked a
t the same as me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yet you didn't like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Well he was all right. You know, he'd pass remarks while he shouldn't pass remarks you know. Things that made you feel - ooh - I would like to slap him across - he didn't care. He - he was supposed to be a toff and all. Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 This is about people who lived in Shildon now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh no, I don't know many people there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Who were considered the most important people in Shildon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 That I knew? Well I should think the doctors and - and Nurse - wh
at did they call here. Nurse - she's dead now. I think they were the most important there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you come into contact with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Why do you think they were considered important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Because they were people that wanted to do good in the world and did do good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What do you mean by doing good?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well if they could help you in any way they would. Nurse Nelson and Doctor Smeddle were two grand people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Who did the shopkeepers in Shildon have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 The shopkeepers, well I don't know. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What about the clergy, who did they associate with, who did they have for friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 they each}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  had their visit - they visited their own church people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What about the teachers, would you ever notice who the teachers had for friends in Shildon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Or the farmers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  know any farmers in Shildon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Who would the employers associated with, the bosses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 The bosses of who? Now that's something I couldn't say because I wasn't in Shildon only two year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What sort of people would you say went to church in Shildon and which went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well we're all one lot, we used to split up, some went to chapel, some went to church, some went to Methodist. We were all good friends.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 What type of person would you say went to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well ordinary people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
Where you lived at that time in Shildon did all the people in the working class have the same standard of living or would you say there were different groups even within the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, where I lived we were all - we were ordinary men.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Do you think that one group ever felt itself superior to the rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, not a bit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 In Shildon were some families thought of as rough and some as respectable?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No, I never knew a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 rough}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  family in Shildon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Do you remember a distinction between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 I think - I don't know, I couldn't say Doris. I know - they always used to try and put - the big man used to try and push the litt
le man down, they never give him a chance.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Your husband wasn't skilled then was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you feel there might be any difference or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh yes, there was a difference. The men that was unskilled was doing the work that - that the m
en that were - were skilled was doing but - they only was the bottom man.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Did you have a struggle to make ends meet at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Well - just went happily along, we hadn't a lot but we were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You didn't really have a struggle then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Your husband was ill the first }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 year}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 , what difference did it make when your husband was ill or out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 That's the first year we were married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you manage then, you didn't have much then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 No. I had me sick money. But I had father behind me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Your father helped you did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 How did you feel about having a struggle at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Nothing at all because I had me father and me brother behind me all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Was that the only time your husband was ill, off work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes, he had about a year of it, he never had anything before and he was - he never was off again for any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 length}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  of time after that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 When you were married did you ever get help from the guardians or the parish or any charity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Oh no, nothing of that. I've never been that hard up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 You kept Sunday as a day }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 of rest}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539  when you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12221869\charrsid15683539 were married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 , did you keep different clothes for Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes we did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4654119 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Both you and your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid5591740 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 Yes.
\par }\pard \ltrpar\ql \fi-461\li461\ri0\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid4654119 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6965864\charrsid15683539 
\par }}